{"tid":1974768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我無野講又一重大勝利」19歲手足涉藏兩個槌，因一直保持緘默，獲控方撤銷控罪，無罪釋放","createTime":"2020-04-16T05:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:41:19.000Z","uid":230104,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b8c4c4e2105b91da9834e78f2e7b1fd140c0bc","tid":1974768,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"19歲學生1月1日民陣元旦遊行開始前被警方截查，涉藏有兩個槌、防毒面具及3對手套等物品，被控一項管有適合作非法用途的工具罪，控方今（16日）在東區裁判法院以證據不足為由撤控，但被告申請訟費被拒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告為19歲侍應林子龍，他同時為香港專業教育學院（IVE）飛機維修工程學生。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為被告申請訟費時表示，警方在拘捕被告後不足48小時便落案起訴，被告一直保持緘默，認為警方未有調查清楚，並指出被告當時攜有兩個槌只屬學業需要，事發時遊行亦未正式開始。<br />\n<br />\n控方多次強調，被告當時是在遊行路線內攜有兩個槌，而不是一個，但被告警誡下卻無任何解釋，又表示「若只有一個槌，我就可以坐下（不用陳辭）」。主任裁判官錢禮聽畢雙方陳辭後，認為被告當時是高度有可疑，因此拒絕其訟費申請。"},{"pid":"c2180fd74c115aae3c83ac50ad2d883350441aed","tid":1974768,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"人無事就得"},{"pid":"39be481fae0fa8a76dc8141b52f43d96bcf62947","tid":1974768,"uid":230104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"律政司病入膏肓，訟費豪俾佢執藥啦"},{"pid":"8c69f240895f318a565eae46f5d53a69e8c6556a","tid":1974768,"uid":134087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"其實到今日，需要知「我無嘢講」啲人都知<br />\n諗返被狗打迫供啲手足，我就唔覺得有咩值到打丁"},{"pid":"1868b61b5d771d878bddeec700574f39c8bb26ab","tid":1974768,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c69f240895f318a565eae46f5d53a69e8c6556a","tid":1974768,"uid":134087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"其實到今日，需要知「我無嘢講」啲人都知<br />\n諗返被狗打迫供啲手足，我就唔覺得有咩值到打丁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"無罪釋放就是勝利"},{"pid":"99396adb26f296e7c83769c8ab23fcc1a17a6a55","tid":1974768,"uid":59991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"有幾多單係屈打成招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429e7e06623a37a2a7d7ae13582c4e80eb054633","tid":1974768,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a56b12183abe328d5f130705e5292ffdcfd463","tid":1974768,"uid":103916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"14e93a67d16af76a87db45d3a6a78bb180ad89d2","tid":1974768,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ce17a152dc071673c6fe6576c4a0093890dbaf","tid":1974768,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終都搞到手足上左幾次庭"},{"pid":"a0d0b01d07f6bde461f1f825d03c42530fff289c","tid":1974768,"uid":14422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"因為事實手足真係無辜，緊係冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66585a758871447223ca4412649509ebfac9e835","tid":1974768,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53f22e5be2e90d95693f2443a6776b57c1b11128","tid":1974768,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"人無事呀。"},{"pid":"cf96918d6051d178b2d0c1e82c6459f04f1aa732","tid":1974768,"uid":8830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"我冇野講.gif呢"},{"pid":"be58defa35d16e0ae9a833518519b2d4fcd6aa07","tid":1974768,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"身為一個飛機維修員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb80d97e776f25a0ee560a9ebb659d27158ce2b1","tid":1974768,"uid":63613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"作為飛機維修工程學生  隨身有 兩個槌, 係一件好合理既事"},{"pid":"b0da9e505daba05845117823e9c4084397f7b415","tid":1974768,"uid":112581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"兩個錘有咩問題<br />\n三行裝修是但都5-6把啦"},{"pid":"be7bc26c54186d25b5310420395f5518dd9d87e8","tid":1974768,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"最緊要人無事<br />\n錢銀小事"},{"pid":"fc58fcf9ad59218ab1d72b6c5bf296ff3342d0e7","tid":1974768,"uid":69787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"太好了"},{"pid":"c44238286a5c0ebc23e380ba8d097372ac0a5304","tid":1974768,"uid":63613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJvs047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJvs047.jpg&h=c8766a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"886956290a210ca8162daaeb4e1e1175ae715a5b","tid":1974768,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUCrxfi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUCrxfi.gif&h=c2b8750e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b4bbe1cb4570ea5b6be1ebcdfdc76a0db191154","tid":1974768,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"民陣今年 1 月 1 日發起元旦大遊行，警方於遊行前不斷截查及拘捕市民，遊行其間則因發生激烈警民衝突，警方腰斬活動並大規模圍捕市民，9 人被拘捕，當中一名19歲男子，因管有兩把鎚仔及面具等被控，案件今於東區裁判法院再訊，控方申請撤銷控罪，但反對辯方申請訟費，指被告警誡下保持緘默，且管有兩個鎚子，而非一個。主任裁判官錢禮最終指被告自招嫌疑，拒絕其訟費申請。被告於庭外表示被捕後「保持沉默好有用」，希望被捕者可清楚知悉及行使相關權利。<br />\n<br />\n當庭獲釋的被告林子龍於庭外指，獲撤控屬於其意料之內，因他警誡下保持緘默，且警方倉卒落控，故他與律師都認為控方「鋤我唔入」。他又表示自己被捕前已在網上清楚了解被捕者權利，包括有權保持緘默，故他於警署面對警方軟硬兼施時，亦沒有動搖，除基本資料外，並無向警方透露與案相關的資料。他又強調被捕後「保持沉默好有用」，並指當日共有 20 人被捕，其中一名被捕者疑抵擋不住警方的軟硬兼施，於律師未到達之前已向警方有所招認，結果不獲保釋。林又指雖然案件擾攘4個月對他造成的壓力不算大，因他面對的控罪較輕，但因是第一次被捕，當時仍會感到「好徬徨」，並一度哽咽指「有手足要還押，我都好唔開心」，但他表示事件絕對不會影響他日後參與遊行。林又透露，其律師費由 612 基金支付，對於未能取回訟費，他亦覺得無奈及「唔好意思」。<br />\n<br />\n控方今指，控方未能於毫無疑點下證明被告管有涉案工具的意圖，案件未能達至合理定罪機會，故決定撤銷控罪，但反對辯方申請訟費，並指被告被搜出藏有兩個鎚仔，而非一個，雖然控方同意被告絕對有權保持緘默，當認為如他當時能及早提供解釋，或不會被控。辯方則強調被告並無責任告訴警方他管有涉案工具的用途。辯方今日又透露，被告其實是香港專業教育學院（IVE）飛機維修課程的學員，鎚仔是課程中常見的工具，並指兩個鎚仔的大小並不相同。主任裁判官錢禮聽罷雙方陳詞後，指法庭對是否批出訟費申請有廣泛的酌情權，並認為被告行為自招嫌疑，最終拒絕其訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n被告林子龍（19 歲），原被控一項管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用罪，指他於今年1月1日，在灣仔軍器廠街天橋管有兩把鎚仔、一個灰色口罩、一個粉紅色防毒面具和三對 3M 手套。"},{"pid":"b9c89a470ab1ca31b797162d00ea58908f3e404f","tid":1974768,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb80d97e776f25a0ee560a9ebb659d27158ce2b1","tid":1974768,"uid":63613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"作為飛機維修工程學生  隨身有 兩個槌, 係一件好合理既事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"呢類說話都唔可以喺落口供時講"},{"pid":"68cc1ac7c62b9f1c248c679e3d1d5928ea16e90b","tid":1974768,"uid":223198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"推, 大家真係要緊記第一信條"},{"pid":"3d835d03c3cbd10b278ee7c9b88033d3fc2c91ab","tid":1974768,"uid":282115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"我無野講都會被打到仆晒街<br />\n點計都唔係勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}